en_125308_0	Powers vested with the Presidential Commission of Inquiry has been extended following an order issued by President Maithripala Sirisena.
en_125308_1	A special gazette notification was issued in this regard.
en_125308_2	The Presidential Commission had earlier requested an extension of powers in response to the nature of complaints lodged at the Commission.
en_125308_3	Accordingly the Commission has been granted powers to access bank account records of family members of those being investigated by the Commission.
